EFI_GUID gEfiMpsTableGuid

Detailed Description

GUIDs used for MPS entries in the UEFI 2.0 system table ACPI is the primary means of exporting MPS information to the OS. MPS only was included to support Itanium-based platform power on. So don't use it if you don't have too.
